  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate on which indication patients are offered operative
      treatment for their ventral hernia, and to investigate the natural course of ventral hernia
      in the population of patients not offered operation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
